      Your contribution is making a real difference in providing urgent assistance to those affected by these devastating fires.
      </p>
      <br />
      <p style="
      margin: 0;
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: 0.56px;
    ">Thanks to supporters like you, we can provide:</p>
    <br />
    <ul style="text-align: left;">
      <li>Emergency shelter and food for displaced families.</li>
      <li>Resources for firefighters and first responders.</li>
      <li>Long-term recovery support for affected communities.</li>
  </ul>
      <br />
